universum.studios.android.transition.util

Class AnimatorWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.animation.Animator
      • universum.studios.android.transition.util.AnimatorWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class AnimatorWrapper
extends Animator
    A Animator implementation that may be used to wrap an instance of animator in order to 'suppress' some of its features like pausing and resuming for instance.
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
